          heading: "14. Data protection",
          text: "14.1 Personal data is processed in accordance with KursNavi's privacy policy.\n14.2 For Lead Courses, the contact data entered by the Participant is transmitted to the Provider via email so the Provider can handle the enquiry. LifeSkills360 stores the sending time and delivery status of the transmission; no further audit trail currently exists on the Platform. The Provider is independently responsible for the further processing and storage of the data received and is bound by applicable data protection regulations."
